data.description: Fantastic Opportunity for over 2 acres. Make this home your own!  Renovations started for this rarely available 5 bed, 3 bath double wide manufactured home. SOLAR Panels!! Perfect rental, investor, or homestead opportunity! Re-leveled. Kitchen cabinets waiting to be installed. Paint, primer, floor trim, 3 new bathroom vanities waiting installation along with tops.  One bedroom new floors installed and the rest of the home just waiting for your personal touches. New shower connections. Electric and plumbing reviewed.  Big items already done! Roof 3.5 years old, HVAC 6-7 years, tankless water heater 5-6 years old. Don't miss the retreat out back waiting for doors and completion, and the 2 car garage with covered patio attached. 18 Wheeler Trailer for storage or even sell it after closing! Take your pick - easily finish this property for your homestead, resale, or lease it out. Versatility!!! Going fast at this price! Don't miss your opportunity!
